lead_paragraph: Atlantic City's supporters have launched an ad campaign to reverse what they see as an onslaught of bad publicity about the New Jersey seaside resort, where four of 12 casinos have recently announced plans to close.

headline.main: Atlantic City Aims to Counter Bad Publicity With Ad Campaign
